c: 33
v: 55
t: "Shini tsimbi khubo okhulolana nende basabwe nohomba Abana babu beshisiani, nohomba Abasiani babu, nohomba Abana babasiani babu, nohomba Abana babakhana babu nohomba Abakhasi babu, nohomba balia abemikhono chiabu emilunji chiatila, ne murie Nyasaye, toto Nyasaye ni omuloli wabuli eshindu"